Nominees - Best Actress Nicole Kidman 
2011-01-28 09:58:08 GMT
Nicole Kidman shone in her role as Becca in this year's film Rabbit Hole. She plays the mother of a young boy who has recently lost a child opposite Aaron Eckhart, who plays her husband. The drama follows them try to navigate the questions they never expected to have to answer following their tragedy. The Best Actress nominee also produced the film.
